{"data":[{"date":"20:16 09/07","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Luis Enrique tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/chinh-thuc-luis-enrique-tro-thanh-hlv-truong-dt-tay-ban-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Luis Enrique tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau khi HLV Fernando Hierro t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c v\u00ec th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luis Enrique - HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha (RFEF) m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Luis Enrique tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, HLV Fernando Hierro \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c khi &quot;La Roja&quot; \u0111\u1ec3 thua Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u v\u00e0 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luis Enrique tro thanh HLV truong DT Tay Ban Nha.\" title=\"Luis Enrique tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/chinh-thuc-luis-enrique-tro-thanh-hlv-truong-dt-tay-ban-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Luis Enrique tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Luis Enrique \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi RFEF. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m n\u00e0y, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch RFEF Luis Rubiales cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi ai kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i Luis Enrique. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u00edch s\u1ef1 cam k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a anh \u1ea5y khi s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jose Francisco Molina - t\u00e2n gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a RFEF cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, theo k\u1ecbp xu h\u01b0\u1edbng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c xu h\u01b0\u1edbng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u1ecf&quot;.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Luis Enrique t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft AS Roma, Celta Vigo v\u00e0 Barcelona. \u00d4ng t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 9 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf c\u00f9ng Barcelona, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League 2014-15.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a HLV Luis Enrique tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Anh v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 9 t\u1edbi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wembley.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">La Roja h\u1ebft s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y, HLV Julen Lopetegui b\u1ecb l\u1ed9 chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. RFEF sau \u0111\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n sa th\u1ea3i HLV Lopetegui v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Fernando Hierro l\u00e0m HLV t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hierro phat bieu sau tran TBN vs Nga\" title=\"Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn TBN vs Nga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/cay-dang-roi-world-cup-ldbd-tay-ban-nha-chot-3-ung-vien-thay-the-hlv-hierro.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Fernando Hierro t\u1eeb b\u1ecf m\u1ecdi ch\u1ee9c v\u1ee5 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Sau khi v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc, Fernando Hierro kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0o v\u1edbi \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ch\u1ee9c v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng, Fernando Hierro c\u0169ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c c\u1ea3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao. V\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jose Francisco Molina Jimenez, m\u1ed9t c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00e1c ti\u1ebfp nhi\u1ec7m.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-fernando-hierro-roi-ghe-hlv-truong-cua-tbn-421-190705.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Fernando Hierro r\u1eddi gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a TBN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/xavi-phat-bieu-ve-ghe-hlv-tay-ban-nha-180-190785.html\">Xavi ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rakitic-phat-bieu-ve-iniesta-421-190625.html\">\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 cho\u00e1ng v\u00e1ng khi Iniesta b\u1ecb TBN h\u1eaft h\u1ee7i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-giong-voi-tay-ban-nha-nam-2010-421-190424.html\">\u0110T Anh gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u0103m 2010</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/that-bai-cua-dt-tay-ban-nha-thoi-ky-den-toi-da-quay-tro-lai-466-190370.html\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha: Th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111en t\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cay-dang-roi-world-cup-ldbd-tay-ban-nha-chot-3-ung-vien-thay-the-hlv-hierro-421-190365.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 r\u1eddi World Cup, L\u0110B\u0110 T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ed1t 3 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean thay th\u1ebf HLV Hierro</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1085","checkdouble":"190800"},{"date":"20:50 09/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 9/7: \"Kylian Mbappe x\u1ee9ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/diem-tin-toi-97-kylian-mbappe-xung-gianh-qua-bong-vang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kylian Mbappe x\u1ee9ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea3o l\u1ed9n k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 9/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">AS Roma ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 10 trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Daniel Fuzato (21 tu\u1ed5i) t\u1eeb Palmeiras v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 4 n\u0103m. M\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 97 Kylian Mbappe x\u1ee9ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 97 Kylian Mbappe x\u1ee9ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Phap-thang-tien-tu-ket-World-Cup-Cong-thuc-chien-thang-mang-ten-Pogbappe-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Kylian Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 \u0110T Argentina b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nEden Hazard cho r\u1eb1ng Kylian Mabppe ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh cho danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng cao qu\u00fd. Ch\u00ednh Mabppe g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p lo\u1ea1i Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh v\u00e0 c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 L\u00ea C\u00f4ng Vinh t\u1edbi Nga \u0111\u1ec3 trao gi\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nga t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean l\u1eddi m\u1eddi c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Croatia, Fabien Delph cho r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Anh \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau ph\u00fat n\u1ed5i n\u00f3ng v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa HAGL vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng xin l\u1ed7i v\u00e0 mong ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jordan Henderson c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Croatia v\u00ec d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n kheo. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Jamie Vardy c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng khi\u1ebfn anh ph\u1ea3i v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">BTC ASIAD 2018 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean UAE v\u00e0 Palestine v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ph\u00e2n b\u1ea3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n l\u1ea1i ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u01b0a hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u00e0o v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3. T\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Viet Nam nam chung bang voi Nhat Ban tai ASIAD 2018.\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Cac-chuyen-gia-noi-gi-ve-bang-dau-cua-U23-Viet-Nam-tai-ASIAD-2018-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110T Croatia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eafng Sime Vrsaljko trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Anh. Vrsaljko d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nga \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Beckham l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Raheem Sterling sau nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. Becks cho r\u1eb1ng gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o m\u00e0 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mario Mandzukic \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 kho\u1ea3ng 3.000 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua bia cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n \u1edf th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng Slavonski Brod khi h\u1ecd t\u1eadp trung \u1edf \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f4ng c\u1ed9ng theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 gi\u1eefa Nga vs Croatia.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-luis-enrique-tro-thanh-hlv-truong-dt-tay-ban-nha-180-190800.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Luis Enrique tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tan-man/ever-banega-nut-thao-go-cho-messi-392-190799.html\">Ever Banega: N\u00fat th\u00e1o g\u1ee1 cho Messi?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tan-man/mario-fernandes-hero-never-to-zero-392-190797.html\">Mario Fernandes: Hero never to zero</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/giac-mo-hoang-duong-cua-benjamin-pavard-389-190796.html\">Gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 hoang \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Benjamin Pavard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-mbappe-180-190795.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Real chi 230 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Mbappe?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/mandzukic-canh-bao-dt-anh-truoc-dai-chien-469-190794.html\">Mandzukic c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong></div>