 style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois la chot chan vung chai cho DT Bi tai World Cup 2018.\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois l\u00e0 ch\u1ed1t ch\u1eb7n v\u1eefng ch\u00e3i cho \u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Thibaut Courtois l\u00e0 ch\u1ed1t ch\u1eb7n quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 Ph\u00e1p.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Roberto Martinez tram ngam truoc tran dau quan trong voi Phap.\" title=\"HLV Roberto Martinez tr\u1ea7m ng\u00e2m tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/7.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Roberto Martinez tr\u1ea7m ng\u00e2m tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bau khong khi thoai mai tren san tap duoc cac cau thu Bi tao ra.\" title=\"B\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1o ra.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/8.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>B\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1o ra.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nacer Chadli tung khang dinh dieu quan trong la DT Bi ra san voi tam ly thoai mai.\" title=\"Nacer Chadli t\u1eebng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/9.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nacer Chadli t\u1eebng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kevin De Bruyne la mot trong nhung nhan to quan trong cua DT Bi.\" title=\"Kevin De Bruyne l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/10.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Kevin De Bruyne l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard thoai mai khi tro chuyen voi HLV Roberto Martinez.\" title=\"Eden Hazard tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i khi tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV Roberto Martinez.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/11.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Eden Hazard tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i khi tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV Roberto Martinez.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Bi se cham tran Phap vao 1h00 ngay 11/7.\" title=\"\u0110T B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 11/7.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/12.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 11/7.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-roberto-martinez-noi-ve-co-hoi-cua-dt-bi-465-190803.html\">\u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhan-dinh-ban-ket-phap-vs-bi-421-190802.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 27: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh