2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Roberto Martinez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p khi ch\u1ec9 ra y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng nhau c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 t\u1ed1t trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m n\u00ean x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay&quot; - HLV Roberto Martinez chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0110T Ph\u00e1p: &quot;T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Roberto Martinez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Roberto Martinez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/hlv-roberto-martinez-noi-ve-co-hoi-cua-dt-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Roberto Martinez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u0169ng quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng trong nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eafn k\u1ebft. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft khi g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0110T B\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1986. Th\u1eadt tr\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ecd v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1986 v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 4-2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u1ea3 B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat khi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Euro 2016.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nacer Chadli khang dinh Bi khong ngan Phap.\" title=\"Nacer Chadli kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng ng\u00e1n Ph\u00e1p.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/chadli.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nacer Chadli kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng ng\u00e1n Ph\u00e1p.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, Nacer Chadli kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &quot;N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Brazil th\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u1ea3. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd e ng\u1ea1i th\u00ec \u0111\u1eebng mong \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ph\u00e1p&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1edbn khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Brazil, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp th\u00eam s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u1ecdi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 r\u1eb1ng B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng g\u00ec. B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ed1c gia nh\u1ecf v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng 11 tri\u1ec7u d\u00e2n. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&quot;.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 11/7.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhan-dinh-ban-ket-phap-vs-bi-421-190802.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 27: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pickford-dap-tra-tu-ton-sau-khi-bi-courtois-khieu-khich-421-190788.html\">Pickford \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 t\u1eeb t\u1ed1n sau khi b\u1ecb Courtois khi\u00eau kh\u00edch</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-tran-phap-vs-bi-trung-ve-varane-chi-ra-hai-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-doi-thu-421-190773.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9, trung v\u1ec7 Varane ch\u1ec9 ra 2 ng\u00f4i sao nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-tuyen-bi-tuyen-bo-danh-bai-brazil-thi-so-gi-phap-421-190771.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1: \u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Brazil th\u00ec s\u1ee3 g\u00ec Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hazard-truoc-mbappe-hoc-toi-gio-thi-nguoc-lai-421-190763.html\">Hazard: Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mbappe h\u1ecdc t\u00f4i, gi\u1edd th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/quan-diem-bi-va-martinez-la-nhung-ong-but-cua-bong-da-421-190762.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Martinez l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng &ldquo;\u00f4ng b\u1ee5t&rdquo; c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N.D (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1082","checkdouble":"190803"},{"date":"21:56 09/07","title":"R\u1eddi Arsenal, c\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/cuu-than-dong-jack-wilshere-den-west-ham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Jack Wilshere \u0111\u1ebfn West Ham v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n ba n\u0103m sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jack Wilshere \u0111\u1ebfn West Ham<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">West Ham m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh Jack Wilshere, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. Wilshere m\u1edbi h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 s\u1ebd g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \"The Hammers\" v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n ba n\u0103m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Wilshere \u0111\u1ebfn West Ham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jack Wilshere \u0111\u1ebfn West Ham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/cuu-than-dong-jack-wilshere-den-west-ham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jack Wilshere \u0111\u1ebfn West Ham sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Arsenal sau 17 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London kh\u00e1c, Jack Wilshere chia s\u1ebb: \"T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u1ed5n v\u00e0 th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft t\u00f4i c\u00f3 s\u1ee3i d\u00e2y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 k\u1ef3 l\u1ea1 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh t\u00f4i m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ea5u West Ham. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng k\u00fd \u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ebd th\u1eddi \u1ea5u th\u01a1 khi c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho West Ham, theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Upton Park. T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y \u1ed5n b\u1edfi gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a West Ham\".</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i cho Wilshere khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. Ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Blackburn th\u00e1ng 9/2008, Wilshere l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Arsenal ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Premier League (16 tu\u1ed5i 256 ng\u00e0y).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Wilshere kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 t\u1eebng b\u1ecb Arsenal \u0111em cho Bournemouth m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016-17. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Wilshere tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal nh\u01b0ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 197 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n cho Arsenal, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 14 b\u00e0n. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 34 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n cho \u0110T Anh.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Jack Wilshere:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jack-wilshere-ra-mat-doi-bong-moi-trong-24h-toi-172-190477.html\">Jack Wilshere ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi trong 24h t\u1edbi?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/wilshere-kiem-tra-y-te-tai-west-ham-172-190460.html\">C\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Wilshere ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf \u1edf CLB Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-barca-172-190353.html\">Arsenal b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/wilshere-sap-toi-fenerbahce-sau-khi-roi-arsenal-172-189936.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Wilshere</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/west-ham-chi-ky-hop-dong-voi-wilshere-neu-172-189534.html\">West Ham ch\u1ec9 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Wilshere n\u1ebfu...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/wilshere-roi-arsenal-mesut-ozil-da-cho-ngay-nay-tu-rat-lau-roi-172-189348.html\">Wilshere r\u1eddi Arsenal, Mesut Ozil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd ng\u00e0y n\u00e0y t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)\u00a0</strong></div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1081","checkdouble":"190805"},{"date":"22:34 09/07","title":"Thierry Henry \u0111\u1ea9y Romelu Lukaku tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_u