up-2018/truoc-tran-phap-vs-bi-trung-ve-varane-chi-ra-hai-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-doi-thu-421-190773.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9, trung v\u1ec7 Varane ch\u1ec9 ra 2 ng\u00f4i sao nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-tuyen-bi-tuyen-bo-danh-bai-brazil-thi-so-gi-phap-421-190771.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1: \u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Brazil th\u00ec s\u1ee3 g\u00ec Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hazard-truoc-mbappe-hoc-toi-gio-thi-nguoc-lai-421-190763.html\">Hazard: Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mbappe h\u1ecdc t\u00f4i, gi\u1edd th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1080","checkdouble":"190806"},{"date":"05:59 10/07","title":"R\u1ed9 tin Mbappe b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi B\u1ec9 do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/mbappe-co-nguy-co-bo-lo-tran-dau-phap-vs-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kylian Mbappe c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 khi v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Didier Deschamps l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c tr\u1ea5n an ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mbappe v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nKylian Mbappe \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i s\u1eedng s\u1ed1t. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 20, anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng World Cup 2018. Sau 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, anh tham gia t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Les Bleus v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ki\u1ebfm v\u1ec1 2 qu\u1ea3 penalty.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"R\u1ed9 tin Mbappe c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"R\u1ed9 tin Mbappe c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Ro-tin-Mbappe-co-nguy-co-bo-lo-tran-dau-Phap-vs-Bi-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mbappe c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nPh\u00e1p chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup v\u1edbi B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean Mbappe nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ed9 tin Mbappe c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9. Anh v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp s\u00e1t s\u01b0\u1eddn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i World Cup nh\u01b0 Samuel Umtiti, N'Golo Kante r\u1ed3i Benjamin Pavard c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn trong d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u201cG\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng\u201d tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Deschamps tr\u1ea5n an NHM</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau, HLV Didier Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng xoa d\u1ecbu nh\u1eefng lo l\u1eafng. \u201cC\u1ea3 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp h\u00f4m nay ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho ng\u00e0y mai\u201d, Deschamps n\u00f3i v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Didier Deschamps tin vao suc manh DT Phap.\" title=\"HLV Didier Deschamps tin v\u00e0o s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/hlv-didier-deschamps-tin-vao-suc-manh-dt-phap.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Deschamps kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nLo l\u1eafng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t d\u00e0nh cho trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u1eb9 trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Nga. M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, Deschamps kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. \u201cGi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u01a1i lo l\u1eafng khi s\u00e1t ng\u00e0y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng CLB\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPh\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 thua 30 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 24 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 khi g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 World Cup.<br />\r\n<strong><br />\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-roberto-martinez-noi-ve-co-hoi-cua-dt-bi-465-190803.html\">\u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhan-dinh-ban-ket-phap-vs-bi-421-190802.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 27: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhung-vong-ban-ket-noi-chien-au-chau-421-190775.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 27: Nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u201cn\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn\u201d \u00c2u ch\u00e2u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-tran-phap-vs-bi-trung-ve-varane-chi-ra-hai-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-doi-thu-421-190773.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9, trung v\u1ec7 Varane ch\u1ec9 ra 2 ng\u00f4i sao nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-tuyen-bi-tuyen-bo-danh-bai-brazil-thi-so-gi-phap-421-190771.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1: \u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Brazil th\u00ec s\u1ee3 g\u00ec Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br />\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1079","checkdouble":"190807"},{"date":"06:27 10/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (10/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1072018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0