lay:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u201cng\u1ef1a \u00f4\u201d c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd b\u1ee9t m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1ch v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o caro \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 20 n\u0103m d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi c\u00e1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 Davor Suker, Robert Prosinecki hay Aljosa Asanovic\u2026<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Croatia to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 3 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria, Argentina v\u00e0 Iceland \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D. \u0110i t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i h\u1ea1 h\u1ebft \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Nga l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u00e0 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec1u sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mandzukic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Modric, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i \u0110T Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mandzukic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Modric, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i \u0110T Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Mandzukic-phat-bieu-ve-Modric,-dong-doi-tai-DT-Croatia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Croatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft WC 2018 v\u1edbi c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb Modric</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Croatia, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qu\u00ean nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Luka Modric. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay, ng\u00f4i sao thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 5 tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, t\u1ed1i quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng chung c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mandzukic ca ng\u1ee3i Modric</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nModric \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eed cho gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f9ng Croatia g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, Modric s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u0169 t\u1ea1i Premier League k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i cho Tottenham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric\" title=\"Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Dejan-Lovren-phat-bieu-ve-Luka-Modric-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mandzukic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Modric v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ca ng\u1ee3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMandzukic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Modric tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng World Cup gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Lionel Messi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 trong n\u0103m 2014. \u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Modric trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb \u0110TQG\u201d, Mandzukic n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cAnh \u1ea5y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng t\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ch\u00fang. Modric \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 anh \u1ea5y nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Croatia tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-nhan-2-tin-mung-truoc-tran-gap-croatia-421-190776.html\">Anh nh\u1eadn 2 tin m\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhung-vong-ban-ket-noi-chien-au-chau-421-190775.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 27: Nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u201cn\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn\u201d \u00c2u ch\u00e2u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-se-het-do-o-ban-ket-vi-chuyen-nay-421-190757.html\">Anh s\u1ebd h\u1ebft \u201c\u0111\u1ecf\u201d \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00ec chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/davor-suke-noi-ve-dt-anh-465-190752.html\">Davor Suker: \u0110T Anh may m\u1eafn m\u1edbi tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-dai-chien-nguoi-croatia-lay-messi-ra-doa-tuyen-anh-421-190735.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia l\u1ea5y Messi ra d\u1ecda tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1077","checkdouble":"190810"},{"date":"06:47 10/07","title":"Hazard: \u201cT\u1edbi Real Madrid l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/2/hazard-toi-real-madrid-la-giac-mo-cua-moi-cau-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Eden Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9. Gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Chelsea, ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i cho Real l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real \u0111\u01b0a Hazard v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEden Hazard \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. V\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, anh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i St Petersburg. \u0110\u1ec3 t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi 5 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 th\u00eam gi\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u1ed1 1 l\u00e0 Brazil trong s\u1ef1 kinh ng\u1ea1c c\u1ee7a d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn. V\u1edbi kh\u00ed th\u1ebf c\u1ef1c cao, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. N\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra, \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean Hazard l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Eden Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Eden-Hazard-phat-bieu-ve-Real-Madrid-voi-su-nguong-mo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hazard t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o B\u1ec9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, uy t\u00edn c\u1ee7a Hazard \u0111\u00e3 gia t\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Cristiano Ronaldo (chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Hazard l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Hazard c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sang Real m\u1edbi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Zinedine Zidane, m\u1ed9t th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Hazard, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ed9 l\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Zidane \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Los Blancos sau chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a 2017/18, anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda t\u1edbi Santiago Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard\" title=\"Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/eden-hazard-tu-tin-se-lam-tot-hon-messi-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cReal c\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i gi\u1ea3m \u0111i m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Zidane?\u201d, Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid tr\u00ean beIN SPORTS. \u201cZidane l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Real l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Zidane hay kh\u00f4ng Zidane, chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o tr\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Real v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o m\u00e0u xanh c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y phi\u1ec1n n\u1ebfu \u1edf l\u1ea1i. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, \u0111ang l\u00e0 World Cup. Nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 100 l\u1ea7n, t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u1edf Chelsea v\u00e0 cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-mbappe-180-190795.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Real chi 230 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Mbappe?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/diem-qua-5-ngoi-sao-tan-cong-co-the-the-cho-ronaldo-tai-real-madrid-180-190789.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m qua 5 ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/real-madrid-tranh-gianh-milinkovicsavic-voi-mu-172-190704.html\">Real Madrid tranh gi\u00e0nh Milinkovic-Savic v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/modric-khong-tin-ronaldo-se-roi-real-180-190697.html\">Modric kh\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sadio-mane-noi-gi-khi-duoc-real-madrid-quan-tam-172-190673.html\">Sadio Mane n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1076","checkdouble":"190811"},{"date":"16:19 09/07","title":"Pickford tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 \u201cb\u01a1\u201d Courtois v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/pickford-phat-bieu-ve-courtois.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Pickford ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Courtois v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng thua k\u00e9m b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pickford b\u1ecb Courtois ch\u00ea bai</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, \u0110T Anh th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9. V\u1edbi pha solo \u0111i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Adnan Januzaj, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng G.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Januzaj ghi b\u00e0n, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 cho r\u1eb1ng anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y thay v\u00ec ch\u1ecdn sai v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 nh\u00ecn b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pickford ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Courtois v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pickford ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Courtois v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Pickford-phat-bieu-ve-Courtois-va-nhung-chi-trich-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pickford t\u1eebng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois, \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p b\u00ean ph\u00eda Anh g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, Pickford \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 t\u1ea1i Sunderland.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Pickford ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Courtois v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 h\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng. \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh\u201d, Pickford n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u00ea b\u00ecnh n\u00e0o \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Pickford\" title=\"thu mon Pickford\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/pickford-phat-bieu-ve-courtois.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pickford ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Courtois v\u00e0 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf t\u1ef1 tin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb, nh\u01b0ng 2017/18 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u00f9a th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u1edf Premier League. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh qu\u00e1 thua k\u00e9m so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf (\u00e1m ch\u1ec9 Courtois). T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u00e1c h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5p v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ee1 ng\u1ee1. D\u00f9 Premier League hay League One c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1eed th\u00e1ch kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Pickford \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 pha c\u1ee9u thua ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u1ee7a Anh. \u0110i t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Tam s\u01b0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Croatia, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-de-cao-sterling-truoc-tran-ban-ket-gap-dt-anh-421-190780.html\">HLV Croatia \u0111\u1ec1 cao Sterling tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/davor-suke-noi-ve-dt-anh-465-190752.html\">Davor Suker: \u0110T Anh may m\u1eafn m\u1edbi tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-dai-chien-nguoi-croatia-lay-messi-ra-doa-tuyen-anh-421-190735.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia l\u1ea5y Messi ra d\u1ecda tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/kane-muon-tam-su-la-doi-bong-cuoi-cung-tai-nuoc-nga-421-190734.html\">Kane mu\u1ed1n Tam S\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tuyen-anh-dang-san-sang-lap-lai-chien-tich-1966-421-190733.html\">Tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch 1966</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1075","checkdouble":"190781"},{"date":"16:31 09/07","title":"Sao s\u00e1ng Ligue 1 bay t\u1edbi London k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i gia Premier League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/21/jeanmichael-bay-toi-london-ky-hop-dong-voi-dai-gia-premier-league.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Jean-Michael Seri k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t cao, theo France Football c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1edbi London \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jean-Michael Seri \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Jean-Michael Seri l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Nice. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi\u1ebfn anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jean-Michael Seri k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jean-Michael Seri k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/26/Jean-Michael-Seri-ky-hop-dong-voi-Chelsea-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jean Michael Seri c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf NHA</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/muc-tieu-so-1-cua-arsenal-va-chelsea-dang-dam-phan-voi-napoli-172-188308.html\" target=\"_blank\">Napoli \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Jean-Michael Seri</span>, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Paolo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Nice.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Napoli ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Michael Seri \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c, trong \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00e0 Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Jean-Michael Seri k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t cao, theo France Football c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1edbi London \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng\u00a0v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nFrance Football kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Nice \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea b\u1ecf ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Michael Seri</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf th\u00e0nh London mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Michael Seri, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal, Chelsea, Fulham v\u00e0 West Ham. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jean-Michael Seri la cau thu sang gia nhat cua Nice mua truoc\" title=\"Jean-Michael Seri l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Nice m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/21/jeanmichael-bay-toi-london-ky-hop-dong-voi-dai-gia-premier-league.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jean-Michael Seri\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1eafp thay th\u1ebf Conte \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Michael Seri, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 v\u1edbi Nice ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Michael Seri t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, anh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Michael Seri s\u1ebd n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1074","checkdouble":"190782"},{"date":"16:43 09/07","title":"Klopp l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Daniel Sturridge","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/26/klopp-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-daniel-sturridge.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u00e3y xem l\u1ea1i Raheem Sterling x\u1eed l\u00fd ra sao \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 khi c\u00e1i t\u1ed1t b\u1ecb che m\u1edd b\u1edfi c\u00e1i d\u1edf, khi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, di chuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 v\u00e0 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng b\u1ed7ng ch\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed5 s\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 v\u00ec c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n, khi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 trong t\u00e2m tr\u00ed c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y n\u1eeda n\u0103m.</span></p>\r\n<table cellpacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"padding:10px 0px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" width=\"44px\"><img src=\"/content/images/s1.png\" alt=\"comment left\" width=\"44px\"></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 10px; text-align: justify;\"><em>Raheem \u0111\u1ee7 hi\u1ec3u nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng s\u1ed1ng n\u1ed5i trong nh\u1eefng t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u1ebfu l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ghi b\u00e0n. Raheem c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn m\u00e0 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch th\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1o t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u01a1n b\u1edfi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec1u quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 \u0111\u00f3.</em></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" width=\"44px\"><img src=\"/content/images/s2.png\" alt=\"comment right\" width=\"44px\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">N\u1ebfu HLV c\u1ee7a Mancheter City c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u00ed d\u1ee5 ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i, t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1ebft n\u00ean l\u00e0 pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">C\u00e1i l\u1eebng kh\u1eebng c\u1ee7a Sterling khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i s\u1ef1 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c sau \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-o-tran-colombia-vs-anh-nguoi-thu-linh-phot-tinh-ang-le-421-190324.html\" target=\"_blank\">g\u00e3 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh \"ph\u1edbt t\u1ec9nh \u0102ng-l\u00ea\" Harry Kane</span> c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e1t c\u00e1u ra m\u1eb7t khi b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00e2n anh khi \u0111ang theo \u0111\u00e0 b\u0103ng l\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">\u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea1ch r\u00f2i ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi, v\u1edbi Sterling ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn n\u1eb1m trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00f4 l\u00fd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00f4 l\u00fd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Sterling-o-doi-tuyen-Anh-dang-bi-hieu-lam-va-chi-trich-vo-ly-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u01b0\u1eddi m\u01b0\u01a1i trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00ednh s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u01b0\u1eddi m\u01b0\u01a1i b\u1ecb b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e8 n\u00e9n nh\u1eefng ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3. C\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c v\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Sterling ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Kane, n\u00ean anh s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n b\u1ecb soi m\u00f3i, x\u00e9t n\u00e9t m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u1eaft khe v\u00e0 c\u1ef1c \u0111oan th\u00e1i qu\u00e1.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u00f3 sau c\u00f9ng kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00e1m n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 n\u1ebfu n\u00f3 t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup, v\u1edbi Sterling ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn hi\u1ec3u h\u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y hay ho n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-lai-la-nguoi-hung-harry-nhung-khong-phai-nhu-ban-dang-nghi-421-190658.html\">Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup: L\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Harry, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ngh\u0129!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-anh-vs-thuy-dien-dele-alli-421-190660.html\">Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup: Ng\u00e0y Dele Alli \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Kh\u00f4ng ai th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 anh x\u00e9t tr\u00ean kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a anh trong su\u1ed1t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng trong khi th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Sterling kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng n\u00e0o h\u1ebft, h\u00e3y c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn vai tr\u00f2 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng quan tr\u1ecdng t\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a anh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Tam S\u01b0.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">K\u1ec3 ra m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Sterling d\u00f9 g\u00ec c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y v\u1edbi 23 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Man City trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1i \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t \u1edf ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a anh, th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean tho\u00e1t ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o s\u00e1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling Nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Sterling Nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Sterling-Nhan-vat-dang-bi-hieu-lam-nhat-xu-suong-mu-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong c\u1ea3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, Sterling c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn hy sinh, l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng. Anh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng di chuy\u1ec3n, h\u1ebft d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00f4i khi l\u00f9i s\u00e2u th\u1eadm ch\u00ed xu\u1ed1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi ph\u00eda sau khu trung tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 r\u00ea d\u1eaft kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang c\u00e1ch di chuy\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng b\u00f3ng r\u1ed9ng kh\u1eafp m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Sterling kh\u00f4ng th\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ecb x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh khi ph\u1ea3i c\u1eaft c\u1eed c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 ch\u1ea1y theo \u0111eo b\u00e1m k\u00e8m c\u1eb7p. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3ng h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00ean tr\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Li\u1ec7u Sterling c\u00f3 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o? R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng. Li\u1ec7u Sterling \u0111\u00e3 th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc so v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh so v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng trong hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Man City c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf Liverpool? Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1ed3i.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling Nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Sterling Nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00f4 l\u00fd</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u00edt c\u00f3 \u00fd n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 an \u1ee7i g\u00ec Sterling khi b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-de-cao-sterling-truoc-tran-ban-ket-gap-dt-anh-421-190780.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Croatia kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 x\u00e3 giao</span> khi chia s\u1ebb r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd vui m\u1eebng ra sao khi ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">B\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng n\u1ebfu Sterling kh\u00f4ng ch\u00f4n ch\u00e2n ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00f9ng Balkan s\u1ebd c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 lo l\u1eafng nh\u01b0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1ec1 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb x\u1edbi tung \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Sterling s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 t\u00ednh kh\u00ed thi\u1ebfu quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh? Hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 anh.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#333333\">T\u1ea1i sao Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00f4 l\u00fd?<br>\r\n</span></strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/9/Raz.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#333333\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1073","checkdouble":"190783"},{"date":"16:48 09/07","title":"N\u00d3NG: Hai ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/24/nong-hai-ngoi-sao-den-arsenal-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u1eady t\u1eeb nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o David Ornstein c\u1ee7a t\u1edd BBC th\u00ec CLB Arsenal v\u1eeba \u0111\u00f3n 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ebfn ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 9/7.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lucas Torreira v\u00e0 Matteo Guendouzi</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.&nbsp;V\u00e0 sau c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 mang t\u00ean Stephan Lichtsteiner, Bernd Leno v\u00e0 Sokratis Papastathopoulos, l\u00fac n\u00e0y Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 hai b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ti\u1ebfp theo.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Torreira va Matteo Guendouzi sap cap ben Arsenal\" title=\"Lucas Torreira v\u00e0 Matteo Guendouzi s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/lucas-torreira-972041-15288579744461655481829.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Lucas Torreira (tr\u00e1i) v\u00e0 Matteo Guendouzi (ph\u1ea3i) s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 hai g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong th\u1eddi gian qua v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u CLB bao g\u1ed3m: ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Uruguay, Lucas Torreira v\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U20 Ph\u00e1p, Matteo Guendouzi.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Torreira n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB Sampdoria t\u1ea1i Seria A, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 khi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Uruguay tham d\u1ef1 VCK World Cup 2018. Anh \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Arsenal d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Unai Emery.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Guendouzi \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 19 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai m\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p s\u1edf h\u1eefu. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1eeb tay c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Tottenham v\u00e0 M.U, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi cho CLB Lorient s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo BBC, c\u1ea3 hai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i London \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i Arsenal. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0o x\u1ea3y ra, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng The Gunners s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 hai h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y trong v\u00f2ng 48 gi\u1edd s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1072","checkdouble":"190784"},{"date":"16:46 09/07","title":"Xavi ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/xavi-phat-bieu-ve-ghe-hlv-tay-ban-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Xavi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft anh ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem x\u00e9t k\u1ebf th\u1eeba Julen Lopetegui.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n. B\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Julen Lopetegui k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Real Madrid m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u00f4ng qua c\u1ea5p tr\u00ean, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (RFEF) \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ea1nh tay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau khi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o Lopetegui s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Real h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Luis Rubiales \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp kh\u1ea9n. Sau khi tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng 40 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i sa th\u1ea3i c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Porto.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xavi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Xavi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Xavi-phat-bieu-ve-ghe-HLV-Tay-Ban-Nha-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nFernando Hierro l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00ean ch\u00e8o l\u00e1i \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c La Roja \u0111i t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1edfi Nga sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Xavi kh\u00f4ng bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec Enrique \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau World Cup 2018, Hierro t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5t nh\u1eafc l\u00ean l\u00e0m HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. RFEF d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd m\u1eddi Luis Enrique ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u00f2n tr\u1ed1ng sau m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp c\u1ea5p cao s\u00e1ng nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xavi va Messi\" title=\"Xavi va Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/xavi-phat-bieu-ve-ghe-hlv-tay-ban-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Xavi kh\u00f4ng bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec b\u1ecb \u0110T\u00a0TBN ng\u00f3 l\u01a1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXavi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Anh kh\u00f4ng bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eddi ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 b\u1edfi tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. \u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng\u201d, Xavi n\u00f3i v\u1edbi AS. \u201cTh\u1ee9 2, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 3, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi gh\u1ebf HLV \u0110TQG. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi th\u00eam, ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t cho b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n, c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-fernando-hierro-roi-ghe-hlv-truong-cua-tbn-421-190705.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Fernando Hierro r\u1eddi gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a TBN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-3-cau-thu-gay-that-vong-nhat-cua-dt-tay-ban-nha-466-190435.html\">World Cup 2018: 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-bi-co-the-dan-dat-tay-ban-nha-sau-world-cup-2018-421-190427.html\">HLV B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-giong-voi-tay-ban-nha-nam-2010-421-190424.html\">\u0110T Anh gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u0103m 2010</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ky-world-cup-cua-tay-ban-nha-khong-te-nhu-nguoi-ta-nghi-421-190397.html\">K\u1ef3 World Cup c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ngh\u0129</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1071","checkdouble":"190785"}]}